GetXData version 0.02
======================

C interface to X functions

Requires C compiler, X libraries and X header files.

To configure, modify Makefile.PL, changing the paths in the `LIBS' and
`INC' variable assignments to point to directories containing
installed X libraries and X include files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Xorg libraries
  Xorg header files
  C compiler

